snippet: As Tiger Woods prepares for next week’s U.S. Open, his niece Cheyenne Woods will make her professional debut in this week’s L.P.G.A. Championship.
abstract: Tiger Woods' neice Cheyenne Woods will make her professional golf debut at the Wegmans LPGA Championship at Locust Hill Country Club.
lead_paragraph: As Tiger Woods prepares for next week’s U.S. Open, his niece Cheyenne Woods will make her professional debut in this week’s L.P.G.A. Championship.
